data.description: A MUST SEE HIDDEN GEM!! A beautiful and inviting home in Hesperia, offering a spacious layout! Walk right into a bright and open living area that features a large bay window that allows an abundance of natural light to fill the space.  The kitchen is well-appointed with modern stainless steel appliances, plenty of counter space and ample cabinet storage, walk-in pantry, along with a large granite island, making it perfect for those who enjoy cooking and entertaining. Flowing seemlessly into the dining area and family room, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or casual meals. The expansive layout welcomes you with open arms, featuring raised wood beam ceilings and a cozy fireplace providing plenty of room to relax and unwind. The abundance of natural light fills the room, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. But that's not all - the family room also features French doors that open up to the backyard oasis. Imagine stepping through those doors and being welcomed by a covered patio, the perfect spot for outdoor dining and entertaining. And to top it off, there's a custom built, cozy fire pit just waiting to be lit, providing warmth and ambiance on those cool evenings. Whether you prefer gardening, hosting barbecues, or simply enjoying the sunshine, this backyard has it all! Including RV access/parking on both sides and still leaving ample space for all your outdoor toys!!  The primary ensuite is a sanctuary, with its own brick fireplace and raised wood beam ceilings to add dimension and character. Also, boasting a large ensuite bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Featuring a walk in tile shower with 5 shower heads, built in shelves and a seat for those long days. Or, enjoy relaxing in your jacuzzi tub and soak the day away! Additional room was built for guests or can be used as an office, not permitted. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized. In addition, the guest bathroom has been newly remodeled. To add convenience, this home also features a large laundry room with plenty of storage space, ensuring that laundry day is a breeze. Additionally, this home offers a two-car attached garage, providing convenient and secure parking for your vehicles.  You will have access to a variety of amenities including parks, schools, shopping centers, and dining options. The neighborhood is known for its friendly ambiance and family-oriented atmosphere. THIS BEAUTIFUL HOME IS PRICED TO SELL!!
